#: readme.xrm#naso6.naso6.readmeitem.text
msgid "To enable touchpad scrolling, add the following lines to the \"<tt>C:\\Program Files\\Synaptics\\SynTP\\SynTPEnh.ini</tt>\" configuration file, and restart your computer:"
